<p>With ChartHop, Bramm‚Äôs Chief of Staff can tighten up their hiring process by <a href="https://www.charthop.com/platform/integrations/" rel="follow noopener" target="_blank">integrating</a> their applicant tracking and human resources information management systems. </p>
<p>Applicant and employee data automatically populates in ChartHop, giving Bramm and his Chief of Staff a holistic view of their current state. They can create multiple <a href="https://www.charthop.com/blog/best-practices/scenarios-when-to-use/" rel="follow noopener" target="_blank">growth scenarios</a> for the next year, like what it would look like to bring in a head of human resources in four months versus eight and how the team that supports that role might take shape.</p>
<p>Chiefs of Staff can leverage tools like ChartHop to unite platforms and centralize information. It creates a single source of truth that departments can use to collaborate and also helps make processes more efficient.</p>
<br></br>
<h2>A Chief of Staff makes an impact when it is needed the most</h2>
<p>Chiefs of Staff might not hold that role forever. Some individuals move on to other leadership roles in the company, or sometimes the role evolves into something new. But for a startup, a Chief of Staff can make a valuable impact on the CEO and the company during a critical time in their history.</p>
<p>That‚Äôs how Bramm sees it. ‚ÄúI don‚Äôt think it‚Äôs a permanent position in the company... but at least, at this moment, I think it‚Äôs the perfect role to have during a post-Series A phase.‚Äù</p></div>";s:10:"post_title";s:48:"Why every growing startup needs a Chief of Staff";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:135:"For startups, so much happens at once and the CEO can‚Äôt be there for all of it. Sound familiar? You might just need a chief of staff.";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:87:"httpswww-charthop-comblogbest-practiceswhy-every-growing-startup-needs-a-chief-of-staff";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2022-05-02 10:45:46";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2022-05-02 10:45:46";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:128:"https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/resources/%content_type%/%resource_category%/why-every-growing-startup-needs-a-chief-of-staff/";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:9:"resources";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}}